      <title>欧洲投资银行向西班牙洪水灾区提供 9 亿欧元援助</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/european-investment-bank-give-900-mln-euros-flood-hit-spain-2024-11-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲投资银行周三宣布了一项价值 9 亿欧元的金融援助计划，以帮助西班牙在上周发生的严重洪水灾害中恢复和重建工作，此次洪水袭击了东部地区瓦伦西亚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/european-investment-bank-give-900-mln-euros-flood-hit-spain-2024-11-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:38:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
