      <title>独家：文件显示欧盟监管机构调查 Visa、万事达卡费用是否损害零售商利益</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/eu-regulators-investigate-if-visa-mastercard-fees-harm-retailers-document-shows-2024-11-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社看到的一份欧盟文件显示，欧盟反垄断监管机构正在调查 Visa 和万事达卡收取的费用是否对零售商产生负面影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/eu-regulators-investigate-if-visa-mastercard-fees-harm-retailers-document-shows-2024-11-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 17:24:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
