      <title>9 个月净利润跃升后，Banco BPM 2024 年每股收益或超过预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/banco-bpm-may-beat-guidance-2024-eps-after-9-month-net-profit-jump-2024-11-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Banco BPM 周三表示，该银行前九个月净利润较上年同期增长 79.8%，有望超过 2024 年每股收益 (EPS) 预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/banco-bpm-may-beat-guidance-2024-eps-after-9-month-net-profit-jump-2024-11-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 16:59:42 GMT</pubDate>
